Summary: Biochemical reaction from olanzapine to olanzapine n-oxide. This interaction can be catalyzed by FMO1, CYP3A4, FMO3, CYP2D6 or CYP3A5.
Biochemical reaction from olanzapine to olanzapine 4-n-glucuronide. This interaction can be catalyzed by UGT1A4 or UGT2B10.
Biochemical reaction from olanzapine to desmethyl olanzapine. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP3A4, CYP2C8, CYP1A2, CYP2D6 or CYP3A43.
Biochemical reaction from olanzapine to 2-hydroxymethyl olanzapine. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP2D6.
Biochemical reaction from olanzapine to olanzapine 10-n-glucuronide. This interaction can be catalyzed by UGT1A4 or UGT2B10.
Transport from olanzapine to olanzapine. This interaction is catalyzed by ABCB1.
